Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"Commutant", "::", "usage"}], "=", 
   "\"\<Commutant may be used to calculate an operator basis for all elements \
that commute with a given set of operators Q={\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \
\(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \(2\)]\), ...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \
\(n\)]\)} with respect to a given Lie algebra basis B={\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\
\), \(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\), \(2\)]\), \
...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\), \(N\)]\)}. The commutant of Q, comm(Q), is \
defined by: comm(Q)={b \[Element] B| [b,q]= 0 \[ForAll]q \[Element] Q}. The \
output is again a set of operators C={\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(1\)]\),\!\(\
\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(2\)]\),...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(M\)]\)} with \
the property: [\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(j\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \
\(k\)]\)]=0 for all operators \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(j\)]\) and \
\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \(k\)]\), in general though [\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\
\), \(i\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(C\), \(j\)]\)]\[NotEqual]0.\n\nThe syntax \
distinguishes two important cases:\n\n1) Commutant[{\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \
\(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \(2\)]\), ...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \
\(n\)]\)}] calculates a basis for all elements that commute with Q with \
respect to all of Liouville space.\n\n2)   Commutant[{{\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\
\), \(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \(2\)]\), \
...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(Q\), \(n\)]\)},{\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\), \
\(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\), \(2\)]\), ...,\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(B\), \
\(N\)]\)}}] calculates a basis for all elements that commute with Q relative \
to B under the assumption that Q is a subset of B, in example Q \[Subset] B. \
\n\>\""}], ";"}]], "Input",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.547025606968602*^9, 3.547025615213552*^9}, {
   3.682594281787702*^9, 3.682594297089982*^9}, 3.7195728001256537`*^9, {
   3.7195729459640474`*^9, 3.719572959449013*^9}, {3.719572991416896*^9, 
   3.7195729920978804`*^9}, {3.728128613908592*^9, 3.72812861900669*^9}, {
